<opener><dateline><date>June 17</date></dateline></opener>
<p>Quite forgot the 16<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
<lb/>Really not an important
<lb/>day at all as the whole
<lb/>matter was settled long
<lb/>before it &amp; tho B.W. knew
<lb/>this quite well no matter
<lb/>what the pr may say.
<lb/> She had no more idea
<lb/>of saying no really than
<lb/>she has of refusing chocolate.</p>
<p> A chocolate wolf would be
        
    

    
         
        <pb n="6294" facs="#L1916_2271_img_6294"/>
        
        
           
            <lb/>quite irresistible. </p>
<p>What I am not quite
<lb/>clear about is what interest
<lb/> <add>16.6.15</add>  you got on your bond mean-
<lb/>while. Does it only cost 
<lb/> £900 or is it not £1000 in
<lb/>which case your will want to 
<lb/>put in another £424 </p>
<closer><salute>Your bw</salute>
<signed>WB Spender </signed></closer>
        
    
                </body>
            </text>

        
            
        
            
        

         

    </group>
</text>
     

